{"tid":1002114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求醫學JJ］ 香港飲食Youtuber 介紹美容院有得驗血？","createTime":"2019-01-30T16:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T17:38:11.000Z","uid":2306,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16b6ef4daeb0f85154bcfb66e37e05cd4b8786c1","tid":1002114,"uid":2306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:46:08.000Z","msg":"我阿媽一直都有睇開youtube &ldquo;兩公婆食在香港&rdquo;條 channel 咁見佢地都係講下飲飲食食無咩點理啦<br />\n<br />\n但係最排我媽比我睇左佢地最近既一段片，係講去左間「養生館」，入面有得做治療同同即時驗血。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sUhjvUi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsUhjvUi.png&h=3a9b3006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但我越睇越覺得奇怪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2dG8pes.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2dG8pes.png&h=b8e1af31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VGktpew.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVGktpew.png&h=66079b93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅血球係咁既樣架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個驗血條友話有重金屬係入面 同埋睇到有宿便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T99NEOz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT99NEOz.png&h=dffeac91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Lvtpfh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Lvtpfh.png&h=7fd37d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住做完20分鐘治療再驗血 就便左上面咁乾淨...<br />\n<br />\n我阿媽問係咪真，我覺得係假野，所以係度問下有無人可以解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得出片介紹唔係錯，但唔好講假野誤導觀眾，好多人真係會信架（好似我媽）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C6nWHL5Ywb4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC6nWHL5Ywb4&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6ltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=40c1fa40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C6nWHL5Ywb4</a><br />\n7:00 治療前驗血<br />\n9:00 講有重金屬 宿便<br />\n21:55 治療後血靚仔曬"},{"pid":"17fbf86960a318bd18fb5232f57428fb56e0bced","tid":1002114,"uid":12604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:47:57.000Z","msg":"唔好睇呢D垃圾啦好心"},{"pid":"fc58286dfca74fbaa6918b8126ff4a3c7570f4bf","tid":1002114,"uid":121077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:49:33.000Z","msg":"攞個腦諗下都知睇血點會睇到宿便<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重金屬就不嬲都有架啦 不過係營養個隻囉"},{"pid":"aecde6a0da6a3200ac9ceeca0695625c43559570","tid":1002114,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:51:37.000Z","msg":"一聽就知係假啦<br />\n<br />\n重金屬呢招好多人玩過啦"},{"pid":"02b0aaa9da46591c1331cfbd0a6939f3a6614ee4","tid":1002114,"uid":2306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:54:04.000Z","msg":"咁佢channel 一般都係我媽年紀既觀眾，信左都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6035cffe4547a986970e55b9bab592b7726f2438","tid":1002114,"uid":234382,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:16:24.000Z","msg":"一睇就知假啦, 邊有可能睇到微生物同重金屬... 廢老真係廢老, 咁nonsense既野都sell一餐, 真係當而家D人傻既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746826b6170c6a8c507a940586dc15088424b9a5","tid":1002114,"uid":234382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"重有 其實嚴淑明係邊個?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問左姨媽姑姐都冇人知, 間野十成十係佢開架啦, 係度搵人笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8ea6054fc13c418cae9e8d491e6146e2c1c21b","tid":1002114,"uid":2306,"like":0,"dislike":0